<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="function-arguments" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#function-arguments"><span>Function Arguments</span></a></h2>
<p>You can call a function by using the following types of formal arguments âˆ’</p>
<ul>
<li>Required arguments</li>
